posts.post_title: Boston Nationals Franchise Type Set Want List
posts.post_content:
Hi, I'm building a Boston Nationals Type Set and am willing to consider any Boston N.L. player from the following sets:

1886 Red Stocking Cigar
1887 N28 Allen & Ginter
1887 N175 Gypsy Queen
1887 N693 Kalamazoo Team Bats Team Card
1887 Tobin Lithographs
1888 E223 G & B Chewing Gum
1888 N43 Allen & Ginter
1888 N403 Yum Yum
1888 WG1 Game Card
1889 G.Waldon Smith
1890 G.Waldon Smith Players League Cabinets
1894 N142 Duke Honest Cabinet


I'm looking to buy or trade for a player from each of those sets.

Thanks!

I have a trimmed N173 of Quinn's scarcest pose if you are interested (after many years I upgraded to a full cabinet). I assume from your list that you already have taken care of the Old Judge. Please respond back to [url]oldjudge@gmail.com[/url]

Jay
Thanks for the offer, but I don't collect trimmed cards or those with pinholes.
